+# ADR-DB-010: Delta Security Model
+
+**Status**: Proposed
+**Date**: 2026-01-28
+**Authors**: RuVector Architecture Team
+**Deciders**: Architecture Review Board, Security Team
+**Parent**: ADR-DB-001 Delta Behavior Core Architecture
